            </span>
            <span class="faq2-icon">
              <svg class="faq2-arrow" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <path d="M5 7l5 6 5-6" stroke="black" stroke-width="2" fill="none"
